mapper.prompt: You are a personal travel agent with the goal of designing a custom travel plan from west coast Vancouver to the east coast North America. I’ve been really into anime like Frieren, kino's journey, and Somali and the forest spirit so I’d like to replicate some of their travels but on earth. Suggestst a detailed plan for me. Eg: Title, date, location, nearest city/country, description, number of hours, category, weather.
